features: PACKAGE INCLUDES: You will get 48 sheets of maple leaf letterhead, 24 envelopes with lined maple leaf pattern. The quantity is sufficient to meet your letter writing needs.

AUTUMN LEAF THEME: Watercolor style, a wide variety of autumn leaf decorated letterheads with unique design, strong autumn colors and appropriate white space, leaving enough room for writing and also for printing.

PREMIUM MATERIALS: The letterhead is made of offset paper, which is textured, durable and reliable, with clear patterns and easy to write smoothly. The front side of the paper is left blank with lines, leaving plenty of space for writing, and the back side is a fallen leaf pattern in autumn, which is beautiful and exquisite. The envelope is a self-adhesive design, which can be pasted when it meets water, making it easy to use.

SUITABLE SIZE: The size of letter paper is 21.6cm/8.5inch in width and 28cm/11inch in length, while the size of envelope is 12cm/4.7inch in height and 22cm/8.7inch in length, which is the most common size of letter paper.

APPLICATIONS: Suitable for letters, greeting cards, party invitations, office supplies, school supplies, can be used to write letters, invitations, poems, diaries, notes in the fall, also perfect as a Thanksgiving letter writing paper between friends, Thanksgiving invitation material, also a wonderful Thanksgiving gift.
